*.jpg    binary
*.jpeg   binary
*.gif    binary
*.ico    binary
*.pdf    binary
*.zip    binary
*.gz     binary
*.tar    binary
*.woff   binary
*.woff2  binary
*.eot    binary
*.ttf    binary
*.otf    binary
